Step_Description.Step_Description_label: Create an administrator context called "AdminContext" and store it in D:\OrchestraFrameworkTests\Administrator

Step_ExpectedResult.Step_ExpectedResult_label: The "AdminContext" administrator context is displayed within the context viewer

Step_Description.Step_Description_label: Create a "Category0" category within the "AdminContext" context
Click on the "File" menu and select "Save"
Select the administrator mode by clicking on the "Mode" menu and selecting "Administrator"
Unfold the "AdminContext" context in the context viewer
Right click on the "Category0" category and select "Delete"
Click on the "Yes" button to confirm deletion

Step_ExpectedResult.Step_ExpectedResult_label: The "Delete" dialog box disappears. The "Category0" category has been removed from the "AdminContext" in the context viewer

Step_Description.Step_Description_label: Create an administrator context called "AdminContext" and store it in D:\OrchestraFrameworkTests\Administrator
Select the user mode by clicking on the "Mode" menu and selecting "User"
Create a participation to the "AdminContext" administrator context called "Participation to AdminContext"
Create a "Category0" category within the "Participation to AdminContext" context
Unfold the "Participation to AdminContext" context in the context viewer
Right click on the "Category0" category and select "Delete"
Click on the "Yes" button to confirm deletion

Step_ExpectedResult.Step_ExpectedResult_label: The "Delete" dialog box disappears. The "Category0" category has been removed from the "Participation to AdminContext" in the context viewer
